(194, 1, '2020-03-29 19:25:21', '2020-03-29 11:25:21', '<blockquote>转载自： <a href="https://www.91wordpress.com/924.html">https://www.91wordpress.com/924.html</a></blockquote>\r\n<div class="post-content page-content">\r\n\r\n在使用<a href="https://www.91wordpress.com">WordPress建站</a>的过程中，我们发现WordPress本身的自动保存和修订版本功能，很容易造成数据库出现大量冗余信息。假设我们修订三遍，自动保存两遍，那么就会产生五条数据，而只有一条数据会在前台，另外的四条会成为冗余数据白白占用宝贵的数据库空间。每篇文章的ID不具备规则性，每新增一个修订版本文章ID后会自动加1。WordPres网站时间久了，数据库中会出现上千条冗余数据，数据库会变得非常庞大。\r\n\r\n这篇WordPress教程中，我们就向大家介绍一下WordPress中禁用自动保存和修订版本的方法。\r\n\r\n切换到网站更目录，打开wp-config.php文件，找到ABSPATH，在这之前加入以下代码：\r\n\r\n<!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->\r\n<div id="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" style="margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover">\r\n<div class="crayon-toolbar" style="font-size: 12px !important; height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important; margin-top: -18px; display: none; position: absolute; z-index: 2;" data-settings=" mouseover overlay hide delay">\r\n\r\n<span class="crayon-title">wp-config.php</span>\r\n<div class="crayon-tools" style="font-size: 12px !important; height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important;">\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-nums-button crayon-pressed" title="Toggle Line Numbers">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-plain-button" title="Toggle Plain Code">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-wrap-button" title="Toggle Line Wrap">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-expand-button" style="display: none;" title="Expand Code">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-copy-button" title="Copy">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-popup-button" title="Open Code In New Window">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class="crayon-language">PHP</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-info" style="min-height: 16.8px !important; line-height: 16.8px !important;"></div>\r\n<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea class="crayon-plain print-no" style="tab-size: 4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; z-index: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;" readonly="readonly" wrap="soft" data-settings="dblclick">define( ''AUTOSAVE_INTERVAL'', 60*60*60*24*365 ); // one year&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\ndefine( ''EMPTY_TRASH_DAYS'',  0 ); // zero days&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\ndefine( ''WP_POST_REVISIONS'', false ); // no revisions</textarea></div>\r\n<div class="crayon-main" style="position: relative; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;">\r\n<table class="crayon-table">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="crayon-row">\r\n<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="show">\r\n<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;">\r\n<div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117-1">1</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-num crayon-striped-num" data-line="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117-2">2</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117-3">3</div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n<td class="crayon-code">\r\n<div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size: 4; -o-tab-size: 4; -webkit-tab-size: 4; tab-size: 4;">\r\n<div id="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117-1" class="crayon-line"><span class="crayon-e">define</span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span> <span class="crayon-s">''AUTOSAVE_INTERVAL''</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span> <span class="crayon-cn">60</span><span class="crayon-o">*</span><span class="crayon-cn">60</span><span class="crayon-o">*</span><span class="crayon-cn">60</span><span class="crayon-o">*</span><span class="crayon-cn">24</span><span class="crayon-o">*</span><span class="crayon-cn">365</span> <span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span> <span class="crayon-c">// one year</span></div>\r\n<div id="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117-2" class="crayon-line crayon-striped-line"><span class="crayon-e">define</span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span> <span class="crayon-s">''EMPTY_TRASH_DAYS''</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span> <span class="crayon-cn">0</span> <span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span> <span class="crayon-c">// zero days</span></div>\r\n<div id="crayon-5e8084a797877377355117-3" class="crayon-line"><span class="crayon-e">define</span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span> <span class="crayon-s">''WP_POST_REVISIONS''</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span> <span class="crayon-t">false</span> <span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span> <span class="crayon-c">// no revisions</span></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- [Format Time: 0.0018 seconds] -->\r\n\r\n赶紧加入以上代码进行测试吧。\r\n\r\n当然如果您的网站中没有加入上面的代码，您可以使用我们前面介绍的方法来清空数据表中的自动保存和修订版本信息。详细的操作方法请点击如下链接：\r\nWordPress网站数据库优化技巧\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n</div>', 'wordpress教程：禁用自动保存和修订版本', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress%e6%95%99%e7%a8%8b%ef%bc%9a%e7%a6%81%e7%94%a8%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e4%bf%9d%e5%ad%98%e5%92%8c%e4%bf%ae%e8%ae%a2%e7%89%88%e6%9c%ac', '', '', '2020-04-09 12:27:23', '2020-04-09 04:27:23', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=194', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(195, 1, '2020-03-29 19:31:47', '2020-03-29 11:31:47', '使用WordPress做完网站以后，当我们查看网站源代码的时候，发现WordPress调用自身或插件的CSS文件和JS文件的后方都带着版本号，如下图：\r\n<div class="post-content page-content">\r\n\r\n<code>&lt;link rel=''stylesheet'' id=''_fontawesome-css'' href=''https://seniortesting.club/wp-content/themes/test/css/font-awesome.min.css?ver=6.0'' type=''text/css'' media=''all'' /&gt;</code>\r\n\r\n这样看起来既不美观，又暴漏了我们使用的WordPress的信息。这篇<a href="https://seniortesting.club/%e4%b8%89%e6%ad%a5%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3wordpress%e6%96%b0%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e8%ae%bf%e9%97%ae%e6%85%a2%e7%9a%84%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98%ef%bc%8c%e8%ae%a9%e6%82%a8%e7%9a%84%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e5%81%a5%e6%ad%a5/">WordPress教程</a>里我们将向大家介绍一下如何移除WordPress调用的CSS和JS文件后面的版本号。\r\n\r\n切换到主题目录，打开<strong>functions.php</strong>文件，加入以下代码：\r\n\r\n<!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->\r\n<div id="crayon-5e8084ab628e9428346731" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" style="margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover">\r\n<div class="crayon-toolbar" style="font-size: 12px !important; height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important; margin-top: -18px; display: none; position: absolute; z-index: 2;" data-settings=" mouseover overlay hide delay">\r\n\r\n<span class="crayon-title">functions.php</span>\r\n<div class="crayon-tools" style="font-size: 12px !important; height: 18px !important; line-height: 18px !important;">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-nums-button crayon-pressed" title="Toggle Line Numbers">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-plain-button" title="Toggle Plain Code">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-wrap-button" title="Toggle Line Wrap">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-expand-button" style="display: none;" title="Expand Code">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-copy-button" title="Copy">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="crayon-button crayon-popup-button" title="Open Code In New Window">\r\n<div class="crayon-button-icon" style="background-size: 48px 128px; background-image: url(;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class="crayon-language">PHP</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix">\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="php">&lt;?php\r\n  // remove wp version param from any enqueued scripts\r\n  function 91wordpress_remove_wp_ver_css_js( $src ) {\r\n    if ( strpos( $src, ''ver='' . get_bloginfo( ''version'' ) ) )\r\n      $src = remove_query_arg( ''ver'', $src );\r\n    return $src;\r\n  }\r\n  add_filter( ''style_loader_src'', ''91wordpress_remove_wp_ver_css_js'', 9999 );\r\n  add_filter( ''script_loader_src'', ''91wordpress_remove_wp_ver_css_js'', 9999 );\r\n?&gt;</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'wordpress优化技巧：删除CSS和JS文件后面的版本号', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress%e4%bc%98%e5%8c%96%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4css%e5%92%8cjs%e6%96%87%e4%bb%b6%e5%90%8e%e9%9d%a2%e7%9a%84%e7%89%88%e6%9c%ac%e5%8f%b7', '', '', '2020-04-09 13:24:19', '2020-04-09 05:24:19', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=195', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(196, 1, '2020-03-29 19:41:08', '2020-03-29 11:41:08', '<div class="post-content page-content">\r\n\r\n在使用WordPress建设网站的过程中，很多新手站长朋友都会遇到这样的困惑：新安装的WordPress网站，使用的也是默认的主题，为什么访问速度非常慢呢？这篇WordPress教程里，我们就向大家介绍一些方法来优化加速我们的WordPress网站。\r\n\r\n1. <a href="https://seniortesting.club/wordpress-faq/">禁用谷歌字体</a>\r\n\r\n在国内，谷歌的一系列网站被彻底墙，包括谷歌字体 Google Fonts 所在的 googleapis.com，因此我们需要禁用谷歌字体，方法是使用插件来屏蔽谷歌字体，<span class="line-through">或者使用360推出的360网站卫士常用前端公共库CDN服务加载Google字体</span><span class="red">（此方法已失效）</span>。\r\n\r\n2.<a href="https://seniortesting.club/wordpress%e4%bc%98%e5%8c%96%e5%8a%a0%e9%80%9f%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3gravatar%e5%a4%b4%e5%83%8f%e8%a2%ab%e5%a2%99%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95/"> 解决Gravatar头像被墙问题</a>\r\n\r\n调用ssl头像链接或者使用多说缓存。\r\n\r\n3. <a href="https://seniortesting.club/wordpress%e4%bc%98%e5%8c%96%e5%8a%a0%e9%80%9f%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e7%a6%81%e7%94%a8-wordpress-%e7%9a%84-emoji-%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd/">禁用WordPress Emoji功能</a>\r\n<div class="clearfix"></div>\r\n</div>', '三步解决WordPress新网站访问慢的问题，让您的网站健步如飞', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e4%b8%89%e6%ad%a5%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3wordpress%e6%96%b0%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e8%ae%bf%e9%97%ae%e6%85%a2%e7%9a%84%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98%ef%bc%8c%e8%ae%a9%e6%82%a8%e7%9a%84%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e5%81%a5%e6%ad%a5', '', '', '2020-04-09 12:26:10', '2020-04-09 04:26:10', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=196', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(197, 1, '2020-03-29 19:37:33', '2020-03-29 11:37:33', 'Gravatar是Globally Recognized Avatar的缩写，意为“全球通用头像”。如果在Gravatar的服务器上放置了你自己的头像，当您在任何支持Gravatar的博客中留言或发表文章，只要提供你与这个头像关联的email地址，图像就会出现在您的名称旁，头像可以协助识别您在博客和论坛发表的文章。\r\n\r\nGravatar对于网站拥有者，开发者和普通用户全是免费的。每个 WordPress 站点中都会自动加载Gravatar头像。自从谷歌被墙，越来越多的知名国外服务器无法正常访问，Gravatar 头像服务也被屏蔽了，WordPress头像也显示不了了，登录WordPress后台的速度非常慢，解决方案如下：\r\n\r\n<strong>1. 使用Gravatar Fixed 头像修正插件</strong>\r\n\r\nGravatar Fixed 这款<a href="https://www.91wordpress.com/tutorials/plugins">wordpress插件</a>可以通过函数覆盖的方式，重新自定义Gravatar服务器，直接读取www.gravatar.com 的内容，保证正常访问。\r\n\r\n点击下面的链接进入插件下载页面：\r\n<a href="http://wpceo.com/gravatar-fixed/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">http://wpceo.com/gravatar-fixed/</a>\r\n插件安装好以后进入设置页面，如下图设置Gravatar服务器和Gravatar SSL服务器\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-465" src="https://www.91wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/gravatar-fixed.png" sizes="(max-width: 542px) 100vw, 542px" srcset="https://www.91wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/gravatar-fixed.png 542w, https://www.91wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/gravatar-fixed-300x95.png 300w" alt="gravatar-fixed" width="542" height="171" />\r\n\r\n注意：Gravatar SSL 服务器仅适用于 WordPress 开启SSL访问时才起作用。\r\n\r\n<strong>2. 多说缓存，切换到模板目录，打开functions.php，加入以下代码：</strong>\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="php">function duoshuo_avatar($avatar) {\r\n    $avatar = str_replace(array("www.gravatar.com","0.gravatar.com","1.gravatar.com","2.gravatar.com"),"gravatar.duoshuo.com",$avatar);\r\n    return $avatar;\r\n}\r\nadd_filter( ''get_avatar'', ''duoshuo_avatar'', 10, 3 );</pre>\r\n&nbsp;', 'WordPress优化加速技巧：解决Gravatar头像被墙方法', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress%e4%bc%98%e5%8c%96%e5%8a%a0%e9%80%9f%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3gravatar%e5%a4%b4%e5%83%8f%e8%a2%ab%e5%a2%99%e6%96%b9%e6%b3%95', '', '\nhttp://wpceo.com/gravatar-fixed/', '2020-04-09 12:26:41', '2020-04-09 04:26:41', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=197', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(198, 1, '2020-03-29 19:51:38', '2020-03-29 11:51:38', '使用<a href="https://www.91wordpress.com/">WordPress建站</a>完成以后，浏览网站时速度很慢，查看源代码发现有一大段莫名的代码，如下图：\r\n\r\n<img src="https://www.91wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/emoji.jpg" />\r\n\r\n这是WordPress自带的Emoji功能，它的的实现方式是调用 http://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72×72/ 下的图片来渲染Emoji，而http://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72×72/这个地址在国内是访问不了的，所以我们需要禁用 WordPress Emoji 功能。这篇<a href="https://www.91wordpress.com/tutorials">WordPress教程</a>里我们就向大家介绍一下具体的方法。\r\n\r\n切换到主题目录，打开<strong><code>functions.php</code></strong>文件，添加以下代码：\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="php">&lt;?php \r\n  remove_action(''admin_print_scripts'',''print_emoji_detection_script'');\r\n  remove_action(''admin_print_styles'',''print_emoji_styles'');\r\n  remove_action(''wp_head'',''print_emoji_detection_script'',\t7);\r\n  remove_action(''wp_print_styles'',''print_emoji_styles'');\r\n  remove_action(''embed_head'',''print_emoji_detection_script'');\r\n  remove_filter(''the_content_feed'',''wp_staticize_emoji'');\r\n  remove_filter(''comment_text_rss'',''wp_staticize_emoji'');\r\n  remove_filter(''wp_mail'',''wp_staticize_emoji_for_email'');\r\n?&gt;</pre>\r\n&nbsp;', 'wordpress优化加速技巧：禁用 WordPress 的 Emoji 功能', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress%e4%bc%98%e5%8c%96%e5%8a%a0%e9%80%9f%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%ef%bc%9a%e7%a6%81%e7%94%a8-wordpress-%e7%9a%84-emoji-%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd', '', '', '2020-04-09 12:25:24', '2020-04-09 04:25:24', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=198', 0, 'post', '', 0),
