(209, 1, '2020-03-29 21:14:04', '2020-03-29 13:14:04', '<blockquote>WordPress既然有评论的功能，那就肯定有隐藏部分内容的需求！这个功能也也很简单，就几个步骤搞定。这里我把全部代码和详细教程分享给大家！嘿嘿，以后要养成不做伸手党的好习惯啦 ！</blockquote>\r\n<div class="wp-block-aduxq-biaoti qe_bt_zts">\r\n<h1 id="wznav_0">功能介绍</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n在文章中插入一些隐藏内容，管理员可以直接看到。其他人要评论回复之后才能看到！\r\n<h2 id="wznav_1">示例</h2>\r\n[replyhide]这是隐藏的内容[/replyhide]\r\n<h2 id="wznav_2">使用方法：</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>直接在编辑器点击隐藏内容按钮，插入内容就行了</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href="http://blog.qiwe.ink/wp-content/uploads/ycnrbjq.png" data-imgbox="imgbox"><img class="alignleft size-large wp-image-2342" src="http://blog.qiwe.ink/wp-content/uploads/ycnrbjq-1024x475.png" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="http://blog.qiwe.ink/wp-content/uploads/ycnrbjq-1024x475.png 1024w, http://blog.qiwe.ink/wp-content/uploads/ycnrbjq-480x223.png 480w, http://blog.qiwe.ink/wp-content/uploads/ycnrbjq-768x356.png 768w, http://blog.qiwe.ink/wp-content/uploads/ycnrbjq.png 1223w" alt="" width="1024" height="475" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="qe_bt_zts">\r\n<h1 id="wznav_3">详细教程</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n找到你的主题的 functions.php 文件，在最下面增加以下代码:\r\n<div class="enlighter-default enlighter-v-standard enlighter-t-bootstrap4 enlighter-hover enlighter-overflow-scroll">\r\n<div class="enlighter">\r\n<div class=""></div>\r\n<div class="">\r\n<div>\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="php">//添加隐藏内容，回复可见\r\nfunction reply_to_read($atts, $content=null) {\r\n$a = ''#respond'';\r\nextract(shortcode_atts(array("notice" =&gt; ''&lt;div class="hide_d"&gt;此处内容已隐藏，请&lt;a href="javascript:(scrollTo(\\''''.$a.''\\'',-120));"&gt;评论&lt;/a&gt;后刷新页面查看.&lt;/div&gt;''), $atts));\r\n$_hide = ''&lt;div class="hide_n"&gt;''.$notice.''&lt;/div&gt;'';\r\n$_show = ''&lt;div class="hide_n"&gt;&lt;div class="hide_d xs"&gt;本文隐藏内容&lt;/div&gt;''.do_shortcode($content).''&lt;/div&gt;'';\r\n\r\n\r\nif (is_super_admin()) { //管理员登陆直接显示内容\r\nreturn $_show;\r\n} else {\r\n$email = null;\r\n$user_ID = (int) wp_get_current_user()-&gt;ID;\r\nif ($user_ID &gt; 0) {\r\n$email = get_userdata($user_ID)-&gt;user_email;\r\n} else if (isset($_COOKIE[''comment_author_email_'' . COOKIEHASH])) {\r\n$email = str_replace(''%40'', ''@'', $_COOKIE[''comment_author_email_'' . COOKIEHASH]);\r\n} else {\r\nreturn $_hide;\r\n}\r\nif (empty($email)) {\r\nreturn $_hide;\r\n}\r\nglobal $wpdb;\r\n$post_id = get_the_ID();\r\n$query = "SELECT `comment_ID` FROM {$wpdb-&gt;comments} WHERE `comment_post_ID`={$post_id} and `comment_approved`=''1'' and `comment_author_email`=''{$email}'' LIMIT 1";\r\nif ($wpdb-&gt;get_results($query)) {\r\nreturn $_show;\r\n} else {\r\nreturn $_hide;\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n//添加编辑器按钮\r\nfunction reply_to_read_quicktags() {\r\n?&gt;\r\n&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;\r\nif (typeof QTags != ''undefined'') {\r\nQTags.addButton(''replyhide'', ''隐藏内容（回复可见）'', ''[replyhide]'', ''[/replyhide]'');\r\n}\r\n&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;?php\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\nadd_shortcode(''replyhide'', ''reply_to_read'');\r\nadd_action(''admin_print_footer_scripts'', ''reply_to_read_quicktags'');</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n上代码添加了隐藏回复可见的功能，也同时添加了编辑器按钮！直接在编辑器就可以调用啦', 'WordPress增加隐藏部分内容，评论回复后可见的功能【详细代码及教程】', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wordpress%e5%a2%9e%e5%8a%a0%e9%9a%90%e8%97%8f%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e5%86%85%e5%ae%b9%ef%bc%8c%e8%af%84%e8%ae%ba%e5%9b%9e%e5%a4%8d%e5%90%8e%e5%8f%af%e8%a7%81%e7%9a%84%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd%e3%80%90%e8%af%a6', '', '', '2020-04-09 13:21:45', '2020-04-09 05:21:45', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=209', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(210, 1, '2020-03-29 21:56:32', '2020-03-29 13:56:32', 'loading动画大家都知道，很多网站的页面加载都有这样的切换动画， 不仅炫酷好看，还可以让加载等待的时间更加有趣。很简单，一共三步，就能实现本站一样的全局加载loading动画\r\n<h1>第一步</h1>\r\n找到你网站的头部代码，在标签内加入以下代码：\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="html">&lt;style type="text/css"&gt;\r\n.qjdh_no6 {\r\n  transform: scale(1) translateY(-30px)\r\n}\r\n.qjdh_no6&gt;div:nth-child(2) {\r\n  -webkit-animation-delay: -.4s;\r\n  animation-delay: -.4s\r\n}\r\n.qjdh_no6&gt;div:nth-child(3) {\r\n  -webkit-animation-delay: -.2s;\r\n  animation-delay: -.2s\r\n}\r\n.qjdh_no6&gt;div {\r\n  position: absolute;\r\n  top: 0;\r\n  left: -30px;\r\n  margin: 2px;\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n  width: 15px;\r\n  width: 60px;\r\n  height: 15px;\r\n  height: 60px;\r\n  border-radius: 100%;\r\n  background-color: #ff3cb2;\r\n  opacity: 0;\r\n  -webkit-animation-fill-mode: both;\r\n  animation-fill-mode: both;\r\n  -webkit-animation: ball-scale-multiple 1s 0s linear infinite;\r\n  animation: ball-scale-multiple 1s 0s linear infinite\r\n}\r\n@-webkit-keyframes ball-scale-multiple {\r\n  0% {\r\n    opacity: 0;\r\n    -webkit-transform: scale(0);\r\n    transform: scale(0)\r\n  }\r\n  5% {\r\n    opacity: 1\r\n  }\r\n  to {\r\n    -webkit-transform: scale(1);\r\n    transform: scale(1)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n@keyframes ball-scale-multiple {\r\n  0%,to {\r\n    opacity: 0\r\n  }\r\n  0% {\r\n    -webkit-transform: scale(0);\r\n    transform: scale(0)\r\n  }\r\n  5% {\r\n    opacity: 1\r\n  }\r\n  to {\r\n    opacity: 0;\r\n    -webkit-transform: scale(1);\r\n    transform: scale(1)\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n这段代码实际就是全局动画的css样式，有能力的可以自行修改。\r\n<div class="wp-block-aduxq-biaoti qe_bt_zts">\r\n<h1 id="wznav_1">第二步</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n找到你网站头部代码的<strong>&lt;body&gt;</strong>标签，在&lt;body&gt;<strong>之前</strong>添加以下代码\r\n\r\n这段代码就是动画的显示代码了，添加在网页本身&lt;body&gt;之前可以让它先显示出来\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="html">&lt;body&gt;\r\n&lt;div class="qj_loading" style="position: fixed; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 100%; margin-top: -150px; height: 300%; z-index: 99999999; display: none;"&gt;\r\n  &lt;div style="position:fixed;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"&gt;\r\n    &lt;div class="qjdh_no6"&gt;\r\n      &lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n      &lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;</pre>\r\n<div class="wp-block-aduxq-biaoti qe_bt_zts">\r\n<h1 id="wznav_2">第三步</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n找到你网站底部代码最下方的<strong>&lt;/body&gt;</strong>结束标签，在&lt;/body&gt;<strong>前面</strong>添加以下代码：\r\n\r\n前两步已经实现加载动画的显示了，而这一步就是要在页面加载之后让它<strong>不显示（也就是关闭动画）</strong>，总不能只显示动画吧\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="js">&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;\r\n$(document).ready(function() {\r\n  $(''.qj_loading'').delay(400).fadeOut(500).delay(1000, function() {\r\n    $(this).remove()\r\n  })\r\n})\r\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\r\n&nbsp;', '网站添加全局loading动画 超简单实用教程', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e6%b7%bb%e5%8a%a0%e5%85%a8%e5%b1%80loading%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb-%e8%b6%85%e7%ae%80%e5%8d%95%e5%ae%9e%e7%94%a8%e6%95%99%e7%a8%8b', '', '', '2020-04-09 12:22:41', '2020-04-09 04:22:41', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=210', 0, 'post', '', 0),
