(315, 1, '2020-04-09 14:29:35', '2020-04-09 06:29:35', '在查看google的<a href="https://search.google.com/search-console">search console</a> 进入到sitemap看到fetch error提示: sitemap could not be read ,如下截图所示：\r\n<p id="ClbDlCQ"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-316 " src="https://seniortesting.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/img_5e8eb80badda8.png" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p id="XSaWEeV"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-317 " src="https://seniortesting.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/img_5e8eb82403885.png" alt="" /></p>\r\n找到官方的论坛，发现很多人遇到这个问题在新的<a href="https://search.google.com/search-console">google search console</a>平台上,官方说目前还是一个bug，\r\n<p id="KqBwBZs"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-318 " src="https://seniortesting.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/img_5e8eb84b51ff5.png" alt="" />、官方回复是首先在“URL Inspection”中输入你的sitemap地址，然后查看对应的结果，如果结果说是Not Indexed，然后尝试使用 Live Test检查google是否可以抓取它，然后google也可以抓取他，那么就是Pending状态，只是google显示的问题。</p>\r\n\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>我们首先需要确认我们的sitemap是否正确，using one of the sitemap validators online like <a href="https://webmaster.yandex.com/tools/sitemap/">Yandex Sitemap Validator</a> or <a href="https://www.xml-sitemaps.com/validate-xml-sitemap.html">XML Sitemap Validator</a>. If you get a “No errors found” or “Sitemap is valid” message, this means that your sitemap is accessible by others and has a valid sitemap format.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n&nbsp;', 'google sitemap could not be read', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'google-sitemap-could-not-be-read', '', '', '2020-04-10 12:37:32', '2020-04-10 04:37:32', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=315', 0, 'post', '', 0),
