(319, 1, '2020-04-09 15:11:55', '2020-04-09 07:11:55', 'WordPress插件目录中有50,000多个插件，更不用说第三方网站上的数千个插件了，对于网站所有者来说，找到合适的插件来改善其网站可能是艰巨的。\r\n\r\n选择正确的插件对于网站的速度，安全性和用户友好性至关重要。幸运的是，有一些明显的赢家将使几乎所有类型的WordPress网站都受益。\r\n<h2>为什么插件很重要？</h2>\r\n插件是WordPress网站的基础。它们为您的网站带来了重要的功能，无论您是需要添加联系表，改善SEO，提高网站速度，创建在线商店还是提供电子邮件订阅功能。无论您需要做什么网站，都可以使用插件来完成。\r\n\r\n有成千上万的插件可供选择，那么您应该下载并添加哪些插件？无论您正在构建哪种类型的网站，这都是WordPress的最佳插件。\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet">\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper">\r\n<h2>最好的WordPress插件</h2>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper--content" data-type="ordered_list">\r\n<ol>\r\n \t<li>HubSpot</li>\r\n \t<li>DragDropr</li>\r\n \t<li>Yoast SEO.</li>\r\n \t<li>WooCommerce</li>\r\n \t<li>W3 Total Cache</li>\r\n \t<li>Jetpack</li>\r\n \t<li>Monarch</li>\r\n \t<li>Google XML Sitemaps</li>\r\n \t<li>iThemes Security</li>\r\n \t<li>WP-Optimize</li>\r\n \t<li>Contact Form 7</li>\r\n \t<li>Smush</li>\r\n \t<li>Bloom</li>\r\n \t<li>WP Notification Bar Pro</li>\r\n \t<li>Broken Link Checker</li>\r\n \t<li>WP Subscribe Pro</li>\r\n \t<li>BuddyPress</li>\r\n \t<li>PubSubHubbub</li>\r\n \t<li>Redirection</li>\r\n \t<li>RafflePress</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n现在，让我们看看您的网站上必须具有的顶级WordPress插件。\r\n<h3>1. <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/products/wordpress" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HubSpot</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=2250&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=3000&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=3750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png?width=4500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.31.39%20PM.png 4500w" alt="Hubspot wordpress插件" width="1500" />\r\n\r\n没有市场营销就无法发展业务，而HubSpot可以轻松做到这一点。该<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/leadin/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HubSpot插件</a>允许你管理联系人，请按照线索，跟踪转化，建立电子邮件通讯，通过形式和聊天和更多网站访问者互动。\r\n\r\n仪表板和分析功能使您可以评估在发展业务的同时，如何继续做出明智的决策。\r\n<h3>2. <a href="https://www.dragdropr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DragDropr</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=2250&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=3000&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=3750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png?width=4500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.28.53%20PM.png 4500w" alt="Dragdropr Wordpress插件" width="1500" />\r\n\r\n如果您不知道如何编码，那么您就没有技巧从头开始构建有吸引力的网站。但是，聘请专业的网页设计师来帮助可能会很昂贵。\r\n\r\nDragDropr是此问题的完美解决方案。使用此插件，您只需在每个页面上拖放所需的元素即可为您的网站创建页面。有200多种预设计且完全可定制的内容块可供选择。它允许任何人以聘请设计师的一小部分成本创建一个专业网站。\r\n<h3>3. <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Yoast SEO</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=2250&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=3000&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=3750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png?width=4500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.34.33%20PM.png 4500w" alt="yoast seo wordpress插件" width="1500" />\r\n\r\nYoast SEO是WordPress最受欢迎的插件之一。它可以轻松优化您的页面和帖子，使其在搜索引擎上的排名更高。\r\n\r\n使用Yoast SEO，您将获得标题和元描述的模板，因此您可以学习如何根据SEO最佳实践来制作此信息。Yoast SEO还会分析您的内容的可读性和关​​键字，因此您可以在高质量内容与SEO之间取得平衡。\r\n<h3>4. <a href="https://woocommerce.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WooCommerce</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=2250&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=3000&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=3750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png?width=4500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.35.54%20PM.png 4500w" alt="woocommerce wordpress插件" width="1500" />\r\n\r\n想要在您的网站上出售产品或服务？是的，有一个插件！WooCommerce因其无止境的自定义功能而成为顶级电子商务插件。您可以出售从数字文件到实物产品的所有产品，还可以设置货币，显示评论，添加排序和过滤功能，为每种产品设置无限制的图像等等。\r\n<h3>5. <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/w3-total-cache/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">W3总缓存</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=2250&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=3000&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=3750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png?width=4500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.36.47%20PM.png 4500w" alt="w3总缓存" width="1500" />\r\n\r\nW3 Total Cache是​​WordPress最受欢迎的缓存插件之一。缓存是一种存储数据的方法，目的是在用户下次请求时更快地提供该数据。\r\n\r\n本质上，W3 Total Cache减少了您网站的加载时间。由于网站速度的提高，您会发现网站搜索引擎排名的提高，甚至转化率的提高。\r\n<h3>6. <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/jetpack/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jetpack</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png?width=750&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png?width=2250&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-03-06%20at%2012.41.36%20PM.png?width=3000&amp;name=