的比赛或在社交媒体上分享。\r\n<h2>使用插件改善您的网站</h2>\r\n不通过插件添加功能就几乎不可能运行网站。无论您是想通过电子邮件加入表单吸引用户，添加社交共享按钮，压缩图像以提高网站速度，还是要优化内容在搜索引擎中的排名，插件都将帮助您完成您可以想到的所有事情你的网页。\r\n\r\n另外，插件极大地改善了用户体验，这意味着更高的参与度和更好的机会接触更广泛的受众。\r\n\r\n如果您不知道首先要添加哪些插件，这些受欢迎的受信任插件将帮助您入门。', '20个最佳WordPress插件，使您的网站更具吸引力', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '20%e4%b8%aa%e6%9c%80%e4%bd%b3wordpress%e6%8f%92%e4%bb%b6%ef%bc%8c%e4%bd%bf%e6%82%a8%e7%9a%84%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e6%9b%b4%e5%85%b7%e5%90%b8%e5%bc%95%e5%8a%9b', '', '', '2020-04-09 15:23:07', '2020-04-09 07:23:07', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=319', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(320, 1, '2020-04-09 15:20:20', '2020-04-09 07:20:20', '像市场营销中的其他工具一样，您的网站需要定期维护和更新。有时这需要您使其脱机。\r\n\r\n如果您在后端四处乱逛，那么前端的访问者可能会对您的网站感到困惑。为避免对访问者的体验产生负面影响，您可以在进行更改时将网站置于维护模式。\r\n\r\n这将限制前端访问者访问您的网站，并显示一个维护模式页面，该页面告诉他们正在发生的事情以及他们可以做什么。这样，您可以正确设置期望值并保护他们的体验，而无需使您的网站完全脱机。\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet">\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper">\r\n<h2>WordPress维护模式</h2>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper--content" data-type="paragraph">\r\n\r\n当您的WordPress网站设置为维护模式时，只有管理员或您有权访问的人员才能使用或查看该网站。其他所有人将看到“即将推出”页面，其中包含其他详细信息。\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n有多种方法可以使您的WordPress网站进入维护模式。\r\n\r\n首先，您可以依靠内置功能，该功能在更新插件或主题时自动启用维护模式，并在更新完成后禁用此模式。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=300&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=900&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=1200&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png?width=1800&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-12.png 1800w" alt="随着Ninja Forms插件的更新，启用和禁用了内置维护模式功能" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://mhthemes.com/support/knb/how-put-wordpress-in-maintenance-mode/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">资源</a>\r\n\r\n尽管很简单，但是这种方法是有限的。除了插件和主题更新以外，您不能使用此功能，也不能自定义网站前端显示的消息。\r\n\r\n或者，您可以<a href="https://www.hostinger.com/tutorials/wordpress-maintenance-mode" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">将自定义代码添加到您的functions.php文件中，或在服务器上编辑.htaccess文件</a>。对于初学者网站所有者和非开发人员而言，这两种方法都很困难，因为它们需要专业技术知识。一个错误的步骤可能会破坏您的网站。\r\n\r\n这就是为什么使用<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/wordpress-plugins?_ga=2.208099094.56588651.1586188561-1753121421.1568128919" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress插件</a>是在WordPress网站上启用维护模式的最流行的方法。WordPress维护模式插件可让您无需触摸任何代码即可设置和自定义维护模式页面，从而为您提供两全其美的体验。下面，我们将介绍可供您在网站上使用的免费和高级插件。\r\n<h2>WordPress维护模式插件</h2>\r\n为了让您的网站访问者了解计划内的停机时间，您可以使用优质的WordPress维护模式插件。让我们看看下面一些最流行的。\r\n<h3>1. <a href="https://underconstructionpage.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Under Construction Page</a></h3>\r\n<img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=600&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=300&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=600&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=900&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=1200&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=1500&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png?width=1800&amp;name=Screen%20Shot%202020-04-06%20at%205.47.38%20PM.png 1800w" alt="具有Under Construction页面插件的WordPress维护模式页面模板" width="600" />\r\n\r\nUnder Construction Page是一个高级WordPress维护模式插件，用于将您的网站隐藏在自定义的Under-construction页面后面。它是WordPress社区中使用最广泛且得到最广泛支持的维护模式插件之一。它快速且易于使用，允许任何WordPress用户在几分钟内设置维护页面。\r\n\r\n该插件具有从简单显示到全面营销的功能。借助对电子邮件自动回复服务（例如MailChimp）的支持，您可以轻松收集电子邮件并就计划中的网站维护与听众进行交流。\r\n\r\nUnder Construction Page插件提供了维护模式的关闭日期和时间。它还为您的维护模式页面提供了一系列精美的主题，您可以使用CSS进一步对其进行自定义。\r\n\r\n对于搜索引擎优化（SEO），您可以添加标题和描述。您还可以通过添加Google Analytics（分析）跟踪ID来启用跟踪。\r\n<h3>2. <a href="https://elementor.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Elementor Page Builder</a></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=300&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=900&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=1200&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png?width=1800&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-1.png 1800w" alt="带有Elementor的WordPress维护模式页面模板" width="600" /></div>\r\nElementor是一个网站构建器，提供了包含许多功能的拖放界面来创建您的网站。维护模式是最有用的模式之一。实际上，您只需单击几次即可<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/create-maintenance-mode-site-elementor" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">使用Elementor创建维护模式站点</a>。\r\n\r\n有一些模板可以使过程更快，并且您可以分配在此期间可以访问该站点的角色。\r\n\r\n当您打开Elementor的维护模式时，它将告诉搜索引擎您的站点暂时停止维护。它通过以<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/http-503-server-unavailable" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HTTP错误503</a>的形式发送临时维护响应来做到这一点。\r\n<h3>3. <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/fancy-coming-soon-maintenance-mode/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fancy Coming Soon &amp; Maintenance Mode</a></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=300&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=900&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=1200&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png?width=1800&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-8.png 1800w" alt="即将推出的WordPress维护模式模板和维护模式" width="600" /></div>\r\nFancy Coming Soon＆Maintenance Mode插件使您可以快速将站点设置为维护模式。这是一个完全响应的插件，因此它将使页面在所有设备上看起来都很棒。它还提供了三种不同的主题可供选择，因此您可以最好地匹配您的配色方案和品牌。\r\n\r\nFancy Coming Soon＆Maintenance模式易于设置和使用，并带有倒数计时器，进度条，自定义徽标和自定义背景。它具有精美的设计，并且与所有WordPress主题兼容。\r\n\r\n当您继续在网站上工作时，它与MailChimp集成以收集访问者的电子邮件。最重要的是，该插件是免费的。\r\n<h3>4. <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/smart-maintenance-mode/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Smart Maintenance Mode</a></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-5.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-5.png" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-5.png?width=300&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-5.png 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mode%20Plugins-5.png?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%2013%20Best%20WordPress%20Maintenance%20Mo