(321, 1, '2020-04-09 15:26:31', '2020-04-09 07:26:31', '如果您发现网站上有很酷的效果会自动做出反应或响应屏幕上的操作，那么您可能会想在自己的网站上实现这些效果。\r\n\r\n有时，这些效果比美观的功能更实用。例如，考虑一种情况，当您完成不同的步骤时，可以将表单页面上的后续文本设置为显示出来。\r\n\r\n这样的效果使网站具有交互性，使访问者获得整体满意的体验（考虑所有因素）。将它们放在您的网站上可以帮助转换更多合格的潜在客户，并在尚未购买的客户中吸引更多人。\r\n\r\n但首先：您如何指称这些效果？有两种分类。在设计领域，它们被称为过渡和动画。\r\n\r\n您可能已经注意到某些效果似乎更为复杂。JavaScript可以用于渲染这些效果，但是今天我们将讨论将它们与CSS一起使用。实际上，可以说CSS3是设置它们的更有效的方法。\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet">\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper">\r\n<h2>CSS过渡与动画</h2>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper--content" data-type="paragraph">\r\n\r\nCSS过渡与动画之间的显着差异包括几个因素。具体来说，可以通过触发它们的方式，它们如何循环，它们如何复杂，如何指定属性以及它们如何与JavaScript交互（在需要时）来定义这些差异。\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n除了这些主要差异之外，表面上，CSS过渡和CSS动画非常相似：\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>您可以指定解释更改并启动反应的属性。</li>\r\n \t<li>您可以设置缓动函数来控制属性值更改的速率。</li>\r\n \t<li>您可以设置过渡或动画的持续时间。</li>\r\n \t<li>您可以收集有关导致过渡或动画启动的事件的数据，并使用它来改善营销活动。</li>\r\n \t<li>您可以可视化属性更改。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n在我们更详细地研究差异之前，这里有一个快速的过程来确定要使用哪种效果：\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>如果您要进行简单的操作（例如将鼠标悬停在按钮上进行放大），则过渡效果很好。</li>\r\n \t<li>复杂的动画将为您提供更大的灵活性。它允许您设置不同的阶段，以在动画过程中多次更改元素的行为。</li>\r\n \t<li>CSS过渡将允许您使用JavaScript操纵效果。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n以下CSS过渡与动画之间差异的细分将帮助您理解为什么它们在不同条件下效果更好。\r\n<h3>CSS过渡与动画：触发差异</h3>\r\nCSS过渡和动画之间的主要区别在于它们的播放触发器。仅当特定CSS属性发生变化（例如鼠标悬停在元素上时）时，才会播放过渡。\r\n\r\n例如，<strong>：hover</strong>伪类用于更改CSS属性值，使元素根据需要做出反应。\r\n\r\n另一方面，动画不需要任何显式触发器。动画一旦定义就自动开始播放。\r\n<h3>CSS过渡与动画：循环中的差异</h3>\r\n触发过渡时，过渡将运行一次并停止，因为没有可指定重复的属性。\r\n\r\n当然，有一种不那么简单的方式来处理<strong>transitionEnd</strong>事件来实现循环，但是为什么当您仅使用动画时却遇到麻烦呢？\r\n\r\n您可以轻松地将CSS动画设置为循环播放，并根据需要重复多次。您甚至可以将其设置为永久。您可以使用<strong>animation-iteration-count</strong>属性来创建此规范，该属性可以将其值设置为秒数或<strong>infinite</strong>。\r\n<h3>CSS过渡与动画：复杂性差异</h3>\r\nCSS使设置CSS过渡和CSS动画变得异常容易，因此它们的复杂性基于它们的相对灵活性。越灵活，涉及的零件越多。\r\n\r\nCSS过渡直接从开始状态运行到结束状态，而动画允许您创建介于中间状态的元素行为发生变化的状态。这使您可以更好地控制动画中的属性值。\r\n\r\n您可以<a href="https://www.w3schools.com/cssref/css3_pr_animation-keyframes.asp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">定义关键帧</a>并根据需要设置任意数量。播放动画时，每个动画都会轮流命中，并且属性更改将反映在元素中。借助这些功能，您可以创建HTML5动画来与Flash等高级工具创建的动画相媲美。\r\n<h3>CSS过渡与动画：指定属性的差异</h3>\r\n在定义属性值时，CSS过渡通常比动画更“严格”。\r\n\r\n对于前者，必须指定要反映的每个属性。例如，如果您希望过渡影响背景颜色和宽度，则必须为<strong>background-color</strong>和<strong>width</strong>属性指定条目。\r\n\r\n动画使您可以在每个关键帧中指定属性值，而不必声明它们。一旦到达正确的关键帧，该元素就可以平滑地更改行为，即使该属性未在开始时列出。\r\n<h3>CSS过渡与动画：与JavaScript交互的差异</h3>\r\n通常，如果不执行JavaScript，CSS过渡和动画将看起来很棒。但是，在CSS中预定义的属性值可能会限制某些交互。在这种情况下，您可能希望使用JavaScript。但是，如果您不想完全使用JavaScript怎么办？\r\n\r\n可以设置一种混合方法，该方法允许您主要使用CSS，并使用JavaScript管理更困难的方面。在这种情况下，CSS过渡就是您的朋友。通常不值得在JavScript中更改CSS动画的过程。\r\n<h2>CSS过渡示例</h2>\r\n以下是CSS转换的两个示例。图形具有两个确定的状态，动画在它们之间交替。过渡可能有用，但比CSS动画受到的限制更大。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=376&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif" sizes="(max-width: 376px) 100vw, 376px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=188&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif 188w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=376&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif 376w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=564&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif 564w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=752&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif 752w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=940&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif 940w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif?width=1128&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D.gif 1128w" alt="CSS过渡。" width="376" /></div>\r\n下面的示例显示图形通过的多种状态。蒸汽的尺寸缩小，上升，然后消失。该图像比CSS过渡动态得多。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=300&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=600&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=900&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=1200&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif?width=1800&amp;name=HubSpot%20%7C%20CSS%20Transition%20vs.%20Animation%20%5BRewrite%5D-1.gif 1800w" alt="CSS动画。" width="600" /></div>\r\nCSS过渡和动画有很多相似之处。但是，很明显，它们之间也存在重大差异，这些差异应指导您如何在网站上使用它们来改善营销工作。过渡通常最适合简单的从头到尾的运动，而动画则适合于更复杂的一系列运动。\r\n\r\n详细了解<a href="https://seniortesting.club/css%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%e7%bb%88%e6%9e%81%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%97/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">什么是CSS动画</a>以及如何在您的网站上使用它们。', 'CSS动画和过渡之间的主要区别', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'css%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%e5%92%8c%e8%bf%87%e6%b8%a1%e4%b9%8b%e9%97%b4%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e5%8c%ba%e5%88%ab', '', '', '2020-04-09 15:59:22', '2020-04-09 07:59:22', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=321', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(322, 1, '2020-04-09 15:49:18', '2020-04-09 07:49:18', '<span class="">了解什么是CSS动画，不同类型的CSS动画，以及在实际网站上使用的动画示例。</span>\r\n\r\n<span class="">动画是使您的网站上的访问者感兴趣并使其愉悦的强大工具。</span>它们可以使加载体验更具娱乐性，将访问者的眼睛引向页面上的重要元素，并提高可用性。\r\n\r\n通过使用CSS动画，可以在页面上移动，旋转，倾斜，挤压，旋转和拉伸元素。它们可以在页面上反弹，并以各种有趣的方式彼此交互。\r\n\r\n虽然在网络上渲染动画并不是什么新鲜事，但过程却并非如此。过去，动画需要使用JavaScript（这是一种最难学习的编码语言之一，即Flash），这是Adobe产品，您必须支付月费才能使用。在过去的十年中，许多开发人员已从JavaScript和Flash转向使用CSS制作动画。大多数人已经知道CSS —而且它是免费的！\r\n\r\n为了帮助您了解这种Web设计趋势，我们将逐步介绍CSS动画是什么，不同类型的CSS动画以及在实际网站上使用的动画示例。\r\n<div class="post-embedded-module--window wt-blog__embedded-module--window ">\r\n<div class="macro-chapters"><section class="hsg-chapters">\r\n<div class="hsg-chapters__wrapper">\r\n<ol>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h6>什么是CSS动画？</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h6>CSS过渡与动画</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h6>CSS 3D动画</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h6>CSS动画的类型</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n \t<li>\r\n<h6>CSS动画范例</h6>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</section></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>什么是CSS动画？</h2>\r\n假设您要在单个页面元素上使用多种CSS样式配置，例如不同的颜色，不透明度级别，边框半径等。要使元素逐渐从一种样式更改为另一种样式，可以使用CSS动画。\r\n\r\n您可以选择许多<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/css-animatable-properties" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">可设置动画的CSS属性</a>。您可以有一个进度条，显示您的网站加载速度，当访客将鼠标悬停在网站上时，按钮会更改颜色，并且徽标会从屏幕左侧弹出。您甚至可以<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/css-padding" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">为元素的填充区域</a>设置动画<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/css-padding" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">，</a>以在颜色之间切换。这些动画可以使您的网页设计更具凝聚力和记忆力。\r\n\r\nCSS动画由两部分组成：关键帧和动画属性。我们将在下面定义两者。\r\n<h3>Keyframes</h3>\r\nCSS动画的第一部分是一组关键帧，它们指示动画的开始和结束（以及开始和结束之间的任何中间步骤）。换句话说，每个关键帧都描述了动画元素在动画序列中的给定时间应如何渲染。\r\n\r\n这就是关键帧通常包含一定百分比的原因。这些百分比指示它们在动画序列中的哪一点发生。\r\n\r\n让我们看一下<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations/Using_CSS_animations" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mozilla</a>的<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations/Using_CSS_animations" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">示例</a>。假设您要设置段落的样式（&lt;p&gt;元素），使其从浏览器窗口的右侧滑入。对于此幻灯动画，只有两个关键帧。\r\n\r\n第一次出现在动画序列的0％或第一刻。&lt;p&gt;元素的左边距和宽度都已配置为从浏览器的右边缘绘制。第二个关键帧出现在100％（即动画序列的最后时刻）。配置&lt;p&gt;元素的左侧边距和宽度，以便在完成动画后，将段落与内容区域的左边缘齐平。\r\n\r\n在下面的代码和动画中查看<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/what-is-css-class" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CSS类</a>。<code class="css hljs">\r\n</code>\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="css"> \r\n\r\n\r\n   p {\r\n\r\n\r\nanimation-duration: 3s;\r\n\r\n\r\nanimation-name: slidein;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n@keyframes slidein {\r\n\r\n\r\nfrom {\r\n\r\n\r\nmargin-left: 100%;\r\n\r\n\r\nwidth: 300%;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nto {\r\n\r\n\r\nmargin-left: 0%;\r\n\r\n\r\nwidth: 100%;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Caterpillar and Alice looked at each other for some time in silence: at last the Caterpillar took the hookah out of its mouth, and addressed her in a languid, sleepy voice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n<code class="css hljs"></code>\r\n\r\n假设我们希望&lt;p&gt;元素在动画的开始和结束之间做一些事情。例如，我们可以添加另一个keyframe ，以使段落的字体大小随着从右向左移动而增加，然后在序列结束时减小回到其原始大小。\r\n\r\n在这种情况下，代码将如下所示：\r\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="css"> \r\n\r\n\r\np {\r\n\r\n\r\nanimation-duration: 3s;\r\n\r\n\r\nanimation-name: slidein;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n@keyframes slidein {\r\n\r\n\r\nfrom {\r\n\r\n\r\nmargin-left: 100%;\r\n\r\n\r\nwidth: 300%;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n75% {\r\n\r\n\r\nfont-size: 300%;\r\n\r\n\r\nmargin-left: 25%;\r\n\r\n\r\nwidth: 150%;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nto {\r\n\r\n\r\nmargin-left: 0%;\r\n\r\n\r\nwidth: 100%;\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Caterpillar and Alice looked at each other for some time in silence: at last the Caterpillar took the hookah out of its mouth, and addressed her in a languid, sleepy voice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n</pre>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n现在，动画如下所示。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-15.gif 1800w" alt="在从右到左移动时增加动画的段落，然后在序列结束时减小到其原始大小" width="600" /></div>\r\n通过更牢固地掌握keyframes，我们现在可以将注意力转向组成CSS动画的第二部分：动画属性。\r\n<h3>Animation Properties</h3>\r\n动画属性将关键帧分配给特定的CSS元素，并定义如何对其进行动画处理。\r\n\r\n您可能已经注意到，上面的代码段包含以下两个属性：\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>动画时间</li>\r\n \t<li>动画名称</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n这两个属性（指定动画的类型和动画序列的时间长度）是任何动画生效所必需的。\r\n\r\n您可以使用其他属性来创建更复杂和自定义的动画。\r\n\r\n我们将在下面简要讨论每个。\r\n<h4>Animation Timing</h4>\r\n动画定时功能设置动画的速度。要指定动画的时间，可以使用预定义的值<em>easy</em>，<em>linear</em>，<em>easy-in</em>，<em>easy-out</em>和<em>easy-in-out</em>。您也可以使用<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/timing-function" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">三次贝塞尔曲线</a>创建自定义值，以获得更高级的计时选项。\r\n\r\n如果未分配其他值，则默认情况下将<em>轻松</em>设置该功能。缓动开始缓慢，加速，然后减速。下面是一个例子。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=431&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif" sizes="(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=216&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif 216w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=431&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif 431w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=647&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif 647w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=862&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif 862w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=1078&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif 1078w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif?width=1293&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-4.gif 1293w" alt="设置了动画定时属性的圆形" width="431" /></div>\r\n资源\r\n\r\n设置为<em>linear时</em>，动画从开始到结束的速度相同。使用<em>easy-in时</em>，动画的开始速度很慢。有了<em>缓解</em>，它的结局很慢。<em>渐入渐出</em>表示动画的开始和结束都很慢。\r\n<h4>Animation Delay</h4>\r\n使用动画延迟功能，您可以指定动画开始的时间。允许毫秒和秒，正值和负值也可以。正值将延迟动画序列，而负值将立即开始动画，就好像该时间已过去一样。\r\n\r\n例如，如果将值设置为2s，则动画将在加载后2秒开始播放。如果将值设置为-2s，则动画将在动画周期开始两秒钟。\r\n\r\n在下面的示例中，负动画延迟会导致每个圆在动画循环中的不同状态下立即开始。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-7.gif 1800w" alt="具有负动画延迟的圆圈" width="600" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Animation Iteration Count</h4>\r\nanimation-iteration-count属性指定动画将播放的次数。您可以使用数字值使其重复一定次数。\r\n\r\n您可以将其设置为<em>initial</em>以使用默认值（1），这意味着动画将按其顺序播放一次。您可以将其设置为<em>继承</em>以使用与其父元素相同的值。或者，您可以将其设置为<em>infinite</em>以使其无限期地重复。任何将animation-iteration-count设置为<em>infinite</em>的CSS动画都被视为CSS循环动画。\r\n\r\n看一下下面的演示，该演示显示了同一动画的三个版本，每个版本的animation-iteration-count属性设置为不同的值。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-18.gif 1800w" alt="三个animation-iteration-count属性设置为1、2和的多维数据集。 无穷" width="600" /></div>\r\n<h4>Animation Direction</h4>\r\nanimation-direction属性定义了动画的方向。如果使用正常值或默认值，则动画将向前播放。如果使用<em>reverse</em>，它将向后播放。\r\n\r\n要使动画在每个周期都反向，可以使用<em>替代值</em>（动画将首先向前播放，然后向后播放）或<em>交替反向</em>（动画将首先向后播放，然后向前播放）。\r\n\r\n看一下展示下面每个方向的演示。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-16.gif 1800w" alt="四个多维数据集，其animation-direction属性设置为normal，reverse，alternate，alternate-reverse" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://cssreference.io/property/animation-direction/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">资源</a>\r\n<h4>Animation Fill Mode</h4>\r\n使用动画填充模式功能，可以在动画播放之前或之后应用动画样式。\r\n\r\n您可以将此功能设置为四个可能的值：\r\n<ol>\r\n \t<li>如果将属性值设置为<em>normal</em>，则仅在播放动画元素时将样式应用于动画元素。</li>\r\n \t<li>如果将其设置为<em>forwards</em>，则动画元素将保留由最后一个关键帧定义的样式值。</li>\r\n \t<li>如果将其设置为<em>向后</em>，则元素将采用第一个关键帧定义的样式值，然后开始播放。</li>\r\n \t<li>如果将它们<em>都</em>设置为，则动画的样式值将在动画播放之前和之后应用。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n下面是一个动画示例，其animation-fill-mode属性设置为<em>forward</em>，默认值设置为<em>normal</em>。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=513&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif" sizes="(max-width: 513px) 100vw, 513px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=257&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif 257w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=513&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif 513w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=770&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif 770w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=1026&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif 1026w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=1283&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif 1283w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif?width=1539&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-3.gif 1539w" alt="两个按钮，其animation-fill-mode属性设置为forward和normal" width="513" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Animation Play State</h4>\r\n使用animation-play-state属性，您可以暂停和恢复动画序列。默认情况下，此属性设置为<em>running，</em>但是您可以将属性值设置为<em>paused</em>。恢复已暂停的动画将从暂停的位置开始播放动画，而不是从头开始播放。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS.gif 1800w" alt="动画播放状态属性设置为暂停的球" width="600" /></div>\r\n现在，我们对构成动画的不同部分有了清楚的了解。在深入探讨不同的动画类型之前，让我们通过区分CSS过渡和动画来避免常见的误解。\r\n<h2>CSS Transition vs. Animation</h2>\r\n尽管通常将<a href="https://seniortesting.club/css%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%e5%92%8c%e8%bf%87%e6%b8%a1%e4%b9%8b%e9%97%b4%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e5%8c%ba%e5%88%ab/">CSS动画</a>组合在一起，但<a href="https://seniortesting.club/css%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%e5%92%8c%e8%bf%87%e6%b8%a1%e4%b9%8b%e9%97%b4%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e5%8c%ba%e5%88%ab/">它们与CSS Transitions有所不同</a>。一个主要区别是CSS转换需要触发器-例如，访问者单击某个元素。另一方面，动画不需要触发。默认情况下，动画将在页面加载时自动开始其序列。（需要注意的是，一些开发人员将使用jQuery或实现另一种触发动画的方式，但并不需要这样做）。\r\n\r\n另一个主要区别是过渡只能从初始状态移动到最终状态。您不能像动画那样指定任何中间点。\r\n\r\n您也没有过渡循环或向后重复。这是因为，虽然动画具有animation-iteration-count和animation-direction属性，但是过渡没有指定可以运行多少次或可以在哪个方向运行的属性。因此，过渡在以下情况下仅运行一次触发。\r\n\r\n现在，我们对CSS动画是什么（<em>不是</em>）有了更好的了解，让我们看一下称为3D变换的特定子集。\r\n<h2>CSS 3D Animation</h2>\r\nCSS 3D动画（通常称为<a href="https://3dtransforms.desandro.com/3d-transform-functions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3D transforms</a>）打开了图形设计的新领域。借助3D转换，前端开发人员可以为传统网站添加新的维度以增强其设计。\r\n\r\n例如，考虑翻译功能。平移将元素从点A移到B。在2D中，可以使用平移将元素沿水平X轴或垂直Y轴移动。在下面的示例中，黑球在X轴上移动。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=443&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif" sizes="(max-width: 443px) 100vw, 443px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=222&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif 222w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=443&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif 443w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=665&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif 665w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=886&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif 886w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=1108&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif 1108w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif?width=1329&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-19.gif 1329w" alt="具有2D转换功能的动画球 " width="443" /></div>\r\n但是，使用3D变换功能，可以沿Z轴定位元素。由于此轴在3D空间中从前到后延伸，因此可以将元素移到离查看器更近的地方，然后再向远处移动。看下面的例子。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=311&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif" sizes="(max-width: 311px) 100vw, 311px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=156&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif 156w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=311&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif 311w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=467&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif 467w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=622&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif 622w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=778&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif 778w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif?width=933&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-1.gif 933w" alt="具有3D变换功能的动画立方体" width="311" /></div>\r\n与任何动画一样，3D变换不仅仅要让人眼前一亮。如果使用得当，它们可以解决界面挑战并增强访客体验。如果没有战略目的使用它们，它们可能会分散您的注意力并使您的界面混乱。\r\n\r\n现在，我们已经简要概述了2D和3D中的CSS动画，下面让我们看一下不同类型的CSS动画。\r\n<h2>Types of CSS Animation</h2>\r\n由于有成千上万种CSS动画类型，我们将重点放在您会在网络上看到的一些最常见（也最酷！）类型上。\r\n<h3>CSS Text Animation</h3>\r\n动画版式可以立即吸引来访者的注意力。在使用CSS为网站上的文本设置动画的多种方法中，最常见的方法是添加彩虹效果，阴影，毛刺效果和粘稠效果。\r\n\r\n下面是一个手写动画的示例，其中，访问者观看了正在页面上书写的文本。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-21.gif 1800w" alt="使用CSS文字动画的徽标" width="600" /></div>\r\n<div><a href="https://codepen.io/marinamcpeak/pen/XYNdvd" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a></div>\r\n<h3>CSS Color Animation</h3>\r\n您经常会看到网页的背景经过动画处理以在颜色之间交替显示，如下例所示。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=297&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif" sizes="(max-width: 297px) 100vw, 297px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=149&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif 149w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=297&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif 297w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=446&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif 446w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=594&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif 594w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=743&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif 743w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif?width=891&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-14.gif 891w" alt="使用CSS颜色动画的背景" width="297" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://code-boxx.com/css-animation-background-color/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n\r\nCSS颜色动画还可以应用于页面上的文本，按钮，边框和其他元素，使其非常适合将访问者的眼睛吸引到页面上的特定点。\r\n<h3>Slide-in Animation</h3>\r\n使用此CSS动画，您可以从屏幕的顶部，底部，左侧或右侧插入元素幻灯片，以吸引访问者的视线。您还可以将滑入式动画与其他效果结合使用，以进一步自定义设计。在下面的示例中，滑入式动画与模糊的文字效果相结合，因此公司名称逐渐成为焦点。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-11.gif 1800w" alt="使用滑入式动画的徽标" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://animista.net/play/entrances/slide-in-blurred/slide-in-blurred-bottom" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n<h3>CSS Rotate Animation</h3>\r\n您可以使用CSS在2D或3D空间中旋转元素。此动画通常与其他动画组合以显示运动中的元素。以下面的火箭为例。它不仅在三秒钟的时间内从屏幕的左下角移到了右上角，而且在前两秒内沿顺时针方向旋转了70度。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-10.gif 1800w" alt="使用CSS的平面图标旋转动画" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://www.the-art-of-web.com/css/css-animation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n<h3>CSS Wave Animation</h3>\r\nCSS Wave动画是旋转动画的独特用例。要创建CSS Wave动画，您需要创建多个HTML对象来表示您的wave。然后，将旋转动画应用于具有不同背景颜色和animation-timing属性值的每个wave。您也可以尝试使用不透明度。\r\n\r\n效果看起来像下面的演示。 <img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=550&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=275&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif 275w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=550&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif 550w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=825&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif 825w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=1100&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif 1100w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=1375&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif 1375w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/CSS%20wave%20animation.gif?width=1650&amp;name=CSS%20wave%20animation.gif 1650w" alt="使用CSS Wave动画的页面" width="550" />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://dev.to/pixmy/create-waves-with-pure-css-5gp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n<h3>CSS Glow Animation</h3>\r\nCSS发光动画可以为您的网站增光添彩。例如，要在您的网站上推广活动，您可以在深色背景上添加霓虹灯发光文字以设置聚会气氛。您还可以在按钮，边框，加载动画，悬停动画等上使用发光效果。\r\n\r\n在下面的示例中，当用户将鼠标悬停在渐变按钮上时，它会发光，因此单击它似乎更具吸引力。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-5.gif 1800w" alt="使用CSS发光动画的按钮" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://codepen.io/justjspr/full/YbXeXq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n<h3>CSS Bounce Animation</h3>\r\n假设您不希望某个元素滑入。您希望它反弹以进入更大的入口。在这种情况下，您可以使用CSS反弹动画。要对此动画进行编码，需要配置一些动画子属性，包括定时和延迟功能，以<a href="https://css-tricks.com/making-css-animations-feel-natural/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">使元素的反弹感觉更加自然</a>。\r\n\r\n该动画在加载页面上特别常见，如下例所示。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-20.gif 1800w" alt="使用CSS反弹动画加载页面" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://scotch.io/tutorials/create-a-bouncing-page-loader-with-css3-animations" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n<h3>CSS Fade-in Animation</h3>\r\n使用CSS，您可以将淡入动画添加到网站上的图像和文本。在下面，您会看到一个图像从屏幕顶部逐渐出现。此动画对于此图像特别有效，因为它模仿了懒惰地沿河漂流的船的运动。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-8.gif 1800w" alt="使用CSS淡入动画的图像" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://animista.net/play/entrances/fade-in/fade-in-top" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n\r\n为了增强交互性，可以将图像或文本设计为在鼠标悬停在元素上或当访客滚动时淡入。请注意，后者将同时需要CSS和Javascript，因为它更加复杂。\r\n<h3>CSS Hover Animation</h3>\r\n为了增强网站的交互性，您可以<a href="https://seniortesting.club/css%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%e5%92%8c%e8%bf%87%e6%b8%a1%e4%b9%8b%e9%97%b4%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e5%8c%ba%e5%88%ab/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">创建CSS悬停动画</a>。当网站访问者将鼠标悬停在页面上的元素上时，会发生这种类型的动画。您可以使元素缩放，翻转，旋转，甚至在悬停时停止播放。在下面的示例中，CTA按钮的大小会发生变化，并会在访客徘徊时散发出些火花。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-13.gif 1800w" alt="使用CSS悬停动画的按钮" width="600" /></div>\r\n<a href="https://webgyaani.com/css-buttons-hover-effect-animation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">源码</a>\r\n<h3>Infinite Loading Animation</h3>\r\n在访问某些网站时，您会看到它们加载缓慢：通常是标题首先出现，然后是纯文本，然后是图像，依此类推。在其他站点上，该过程将被隐藏，而您将看到一个动画。\r\n\r\n无限加载动画只是您可以在CSS中制作的三个网站加载动画之一，可以帮助减少用户的等待感。由于这种类型的动画使访问者无需指定等待时间即可知道网站正在加载，因此在加载时间未知的情况下，这非常理想。\r\n\r\n这是<a href="https://dribbble.com/Hoanguyen?__hstc=20629287.88744a0080b64d754d91fa9e65d77621.1586417211772.1586417211772.1586417211772.1&amp;__hssc=20629287.1.1586417211772&amp;__hsfp=3114904615" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">设计师Hoang Nguyen</a>创作的。\r\n<h3><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=600&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=300&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=600&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=900&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=1200&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=1500&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=1800&amp;name=Infinite%20loading%20CSS%20animation.gif 1800w" alt="无限加载CSS动画类型" width="600" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Parallax Scrolling</h3>\r\n<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/parallax-scrolling?_ga=2.62813356.1036256435.1585095545-1753121421.1568128919" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">视差滚动</a>是一种视觉技术，在<a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/website/parallax-scrolling?_ga=2.62813356.1036256435.1585095545-1753121421.1568128919" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">滚动</a>时，背景中的元素以与前景不同的速度移动。这会造成深度错觉或“人造3D效果”，以使您的访客的浏览体验更加有趣。\r\n\r\n下面看一下<a href="https://www.w3schools.com/howto/tryhow_css_parallax_demo_none.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">没有视差滚动的演示站点</a>。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=600&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=300&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=600&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=900&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=1200&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=1500&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=1800&amp;name=No%20parallax%20scrolling.gif 1800w" alt="没有CSS动画视差滚动的演示站点" width="600" /></div>\r\n<div>现在，<a href="https://www.w3schools.com/howto/tryhow_css_parallax_demo.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">通过视差滚动</a>浏览该<a href="https://www.w3schools.com/howto/tryhow_css_parallax_demo.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">演示站点，</a>以了解视觉效果有多惊人。</div>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=600&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=300&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=600&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=900&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=1200&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=1500&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Parallax%20scrolling.gif?width=1800&amp;name=Parallax%20scrolling.gif 1800w" alt="具有特定类型的CSS动画类型的演示站点，视差滚动" width="600" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet">\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper">\r\n<h2>CSS动画范例</h2>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper--content" data-type="ordered_list">\r\n<ol>\r\n \t<li>7up Lemon Lemon</li>\r\n \t<li>2016 Look Festival</li>\r\n \t<li>Apple iPad Pro</li>\r\n \t<li>In Pieces</li>\r\n \t<li>Jeans for Refugees</li>\r\n \t<li>Chekhov Is Alive</li>\r\n \t<li>MY / STATIC / SELF</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><a href="https://www.7up.nl/7up" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1. 7up Lemon Lemon</a></h3>\r\n2017年，百事可乐发布了一种名为7up Lemon Lemon的新饮料。为了推广优质的气泡柠檬水，使用CSS动画重新设计了7up网站。结合淡入和摆动动画，开发人员使页面像饮料一样嘶哑。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-9.gif" alt="7up Lemon Lemon CSS动画示例" /></div>\r\n<h3><a href="https://www.kikk.be/2016/en/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">2. 2016 Kikk Festival</a></h3>\r\n代理机构dogstudio每年都会将Kikk Festival的网站重新命名。2016年，dogstudio 使用CSS动画<a href="https://dogstudio.co/cases/kikk-festival-2016/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">重新设计了网站，</a>以创建代表节日主题“干扰”的图像和页面故障。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-12.gif" alt="2016 Look Festival CSS动画示例" /></div>\r\n<h3>3. <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-pro/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple iPad Pro</a></h3>\r\n为了推广iPad Pro，Apple对视差滚动进行了有趣的旋转。水平滚动而不是垂直滚动，您将观察到文本，图像和其他视觉元素以不同的速度移动。这些CSS动画使访问者在滚动浏览页面以了解有关该产品的更多信息时保持参与。\r\n<h3><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=1338&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif" sizes="(max-width: 1338px) 100vw, 1338px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=669&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif 669w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=1338&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif 1338w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=2007&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif 2007w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=2676&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif 2676w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=3345&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif 3345w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/IPad%20Pro%20site.gif?width=4014&amp;name=IPad%20Pro%20site.gif 4014w" alt="Apple iPad Pro CSS动画示例" width="1338" />4. <a href="http://species-in-pieces.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">In Pieces</a></h3>\r\n英国设计师布莱恩·詹姆斯（Bryan James）创造了一个名为“ Pieces”的互动展览，其中介绍了30种濒危物种。James使用CSS动画设计了该网站，使之具有相同的30件作品，当您滚动浏览展览时，它们会按照每种动物的形状重新排列。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-23.gif 1800w" alt="分段CSS动画示例" width="600" /></div>\r\n<h3>5. <a href="https://www.jeansforrefugees.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jeans for Refugees</a></h3>\r\nJeans for Refugees是一项全球筹款活动，由艺术家Johny Darde创建，旨在帮助世界各地的难民。该<a href="https://www.lilo.co.uk/our-work/jeans-for-refugees/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">机构创建星际难民的网站上的牛仔裤</a>无偿支持该倡议。该机构使用CSS动画制作看起来像笔触形式的元素，然后重新形成页面上的单词。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-22.gif 1800w" alt="Jean for Refugees CSS动画示例" width="600" /></div>\r\n<h3>6. <a href="https://chekhov.withgoogle.com/alive" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Chekhov Is Alive</a></h3>\r\n使用颜色和淡入淡出以及许多其他CSS动画，开发人员能够将安东·契''夫（Anton Chekhov）最著名的30个角色栩栩如生。这项个性测试最初是为了让用户可以试听而参与2015年Google对契可夫故事的实况转播，现在仍在直播，目的是让人们找出最相似的契kh夫角色。\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=300&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=600&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=900&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=1200&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=1500&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif?width=1800&amp;name=The%20Ultimate%20Guide%20to%20Animations%20in%20CSS-17.gif 1800w" alt="契kh夫还活着的css动画示例" width="600" /></div>\r\n<h3>7.<a href="https://mystaticself.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MY / STATIC / SELF</a></h3>\r\nJohn Iacoviello的个人档案的主页证明了他作为获奖程序员的技能。尽管最明显的是施加在中央对象上的毛刺效果（它是立体声系统还是硬盘驱动器？），但您可能还会注意到正在使用反射和旋转动画。\r\n<h2><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=600&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=300&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif 300w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=600&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif 600w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=900&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif 900w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=1200&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif 1200w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=1500&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif?width=1800&amp;name=Portfolio%20using%20CSS%20animation.gif 1800w" alt="MY / STATIC / SELF产品组合CSS动画示例" width="600" />使您的网站栩栩如生</h2>\r\n从微妙的过渡到完整的插图网站，您现在可以在大多数网站上找到动画。将3D效果和交互式详细信息作为网站设计策略的一部分可以改善访问者的体验，并使您的网站与竞争对手区分开。', 'CSS动画终极指南', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'css%e5%8a%a8%e7%94%bb%e7%bb%88%e6%9e%81%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%97', '', '', '2020-04-10 16:46:52', '2020-04-10 08:46:52', '', 0, 'https://seniortesting.club/?p=322', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(323, 1, '2020-04-09 15:59:07', '2020-04-09 07:59:07', '<p class="post-header__title"><span>如何设置文字字符的格式是</span><span>营销信息的一部分</span><span>。</span><span>更具体地说，字体在创建</span><span>独特的品牌标识中</span><span>起着至关重要的作用。您可能会注意到与许多知名品牌相关的特定“标准”字体，尤其是在其徽标上。例如，Facebook，Amazon，迪士尼和Microsoft都具有不同的字体，这使它们与众不同。大多数是定制字体和现有字体的变体。</span></p>\r\n<span>在数字时代，使用印刷术作为营销策略，品牌和</span><span>网站开发的一部分，</span><span>也扩展到了网站等在线资源。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>不久前，几乎所有网站上都出现了相同的单调字体，而不论其行业或品牌。实现独特字体的使用非常困难，因为无法在所有浏览器上正确显示它们。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>如今，可以使用各种各样的网络安全CSS和</span><a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/blog/tabid/6307/bid/5586/basic-html-every-internet-marketer-should-know.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span>HTML</span></a><span>字体来更好地树立数字营销工作的品牌。</span>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet">\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper">\r\n<h2><span>什么是网络安全字体？</span></h2>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper--content" data-type="paragraph">\r\n\r\n<span>Web安全CSS和HTML字体可以适应任何设备上的任何浏览器。它们是网页设计中的新标准。Web安全的CSS和HTML字体可确保始终显示正确的字体，即使它们不一定安装在用户计算机上也是如此。</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span>以前，如果用户的计算机上未安装您特定网站的字体，则其浏览器将显示通用字体作为备份，例如Times New Roman。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>这使营销人员对如何将其网页显示给最终用户一无所知，这可能会损害用户体验。如果页面的内容不能完全适应与预期字体不同的字体，则设计可能会中断并导致功能问题。</span>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet">\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper">\r\n<h2><span>Web安全字体</span></h2>\r\n<div class="hsg-featured-snippet__wrapper--content" data-type="ordered_list">\r\n<ol>\r\n \t<li>Arial</li>\r\n \t<li>Verdana</li>\r\n \t<li>Trebuchet MS</li>\r\n \t<li>Times New Roman</li>\r\n \t<li>Didot</li>\r\n \t<li>American Typewriter</li>\r\n \t<li>Andale Mono</li>\r\n \t<li>Courier</li>\r\n \t<li>Bradley Hand</li>\r\n \t<li>Luminari</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span>在下面扩展这些网络安全字体之前，让我们定义一些引用不同字体的常用术语。</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><strong><span>Sans-serif</span></strong><span>是指没有衬线的字体，例如Arial，Arial Black，Arial Narrow，Verdana，Trebuchet MS，Gill Sans，Noto Sans和Optima</span></li>\r\n \t<li><span><strong>Serif</strong> 是指带有衬线的字体，例如Times，Times New Roman，Didot，Georgia，Palatino，Bookman，New Century Schoolbook和American Typewriter</span></li>\r\n \t<li><span><strong>Monospace</strong> 是指字母宽度相同的字体，例如Andale Mono，Courier，Courier New和FreeMono</span></li>\r\n \t<li><span><strong>Cursive</strong> 是指类似于手写字体，例如Comic Sans MS，Apple Chancery，Bradley Hand和Brush Script MT</span></li>\r\n \t<li><span><strong>Fantasy</strong> 指的是装饰字体，例如Impact，Luminari，Chalkduster，Jazz LET，Blippo，Stencil Std，Marker Felt和Trattatello</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span>现在，让我们分解一下这些网络安全字体。</span>\r\n<h3><span>1. Arial（无衬线）</span></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=2250&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=3000&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=3750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg?width=4500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-5.jpeg 4500w" alt="网页安全html css字体arial" width="1500" /></div>\r\n<span>Arial是万维网上使用最广泛的sans-serif字体。它是为希望使用流行的Helvetica字体而无需支付许可费用的打印机而创建的。因此，它们</span><em><span>实际上是</span></em><span>相同的。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>Arial Black是Arial系列中的另一种相关字体。这是一个粗体版本，更适合标题。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>Arial Narrow是该字体家族的另一个流行成员。它具有故意通用的设计，使其非常适合大型文本。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>Arial字体家族的成员被认为是最安全的网络字体，因为它们可在所有</span><a href="https://smallbusiness.chron.com/five-common-operating-systems-28217.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span>主要操作系统上使用</span></a><span>。</span>\r\n<h3><span>2. Verdana（无衬线）</span></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=2250&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=3000&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=3750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg?width=4500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-4.jpeg 4500w" alt="网页安全html css字体verdana" width="1500" /></div>\r\n<span>Verdana在网上和网上都很受欢迎。它类似于Arial和Helvetica，但结构简单，使字母大而清晰。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>字体具有拉长的线条，可能与某些设计情况不兼容。否则，它是Arial的绝佳替代品。</span>\r\n<h3><span>3. MS Trebuchet（无衬线）</span></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=2250&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=3000&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=3750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg?width=4500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.jpeg 4500w" alt="网页安全html css字体trebuchet ms" width="1500" /></div>\r\n<span>Trebuchet MS由Microsoft Corporation在1996年设计。它通常用于网站的正文。</span>\r\n<h3>4. Times New Roman（serif）</h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" srcset="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg 750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=1500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg 1500w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=2250&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg 2250w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=3000&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg 3000w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=3750&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg 3750w, https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg?width=4500&amp;name=HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-1.jpeg 4500w" alt="网络安全html css字体次新罗马" width="1500" /></div>\r\n<span>Times New Roman是衬线字体的Arial。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>它非常流行，并且是Windows设备和应用程序的主要字体。当无法显示指定的字体时，浏览器将还原为该字体。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>从技术上讲，Times New Roman是</span><a href="https://www.linotype.com/259/times.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span>Times报纸字体</span></a><span>的更新版本，该<a href="https://www.linotype.com/259/times.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">字体</a>在印刷报纸上使用，因此，它是世界上最知名的字体之一。</span>\r\n<h3><span>5. Didot（serif）</span></h3>\r\n<div><img src="https://blog.hubspot.com/hs-fs/hubfs/HubSpot%20-%20The%20Best%20Web%20Safe%20CSS%20and%20HTML%20Fonts%20for%20Your%202020%20Designs-2.gif?width=1500&amp;na